1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
<i>Legend of Fei</i>

16
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:07,940
<i>Episode 18</i>

17
00:02:08,550 --> 00:02:10,040
Luckily,

18
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:14,080
I ran into two people
and they led the way for me.

19
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,760
How do you know

20
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:24,230
they would come to me?

21
00:02:24,230 --> 00:02:26,640
We met by chance.

22
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,550
Just by looking at her,

23
00:02:29,270 --> 00:02:32,060
I know she practiced her
internal strength in a wrong way.

24
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:36,310
In Hengyang,

25
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:39,910
only Madam Nichang’s

26
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:42,300
Floating Palm can cure her.

27
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,750
In that case,

28
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,090
you are just in time.

29
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,320
You choose the perfect timing

30
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,830
to take advantage of us.

31
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:53,640
Madam, you are indeed smart.

32
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,450
This girl is badly hurt.

33
00:02:58,110 --> 00:03:00,620
Even for the sake of Li Zheng,

34
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,760
you won’t just let her die.

35
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,420
You are impressive.

36
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,880
You did nothing

37
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:12,040
and cost me most of my power.

38
00:03:12,670 --> 00:03:15,110
You deserve the name of
the Head of Demons.

39
00:03:15,110 --> 00:03:16,630
You are sinister, treacherous,

40
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,910
and extremely shameless.

41
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:22,160
But there is one thing
I don’t understand.

42
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,600
Why did you

43
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,750
take all these efforts

44
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,160
just to see me, a little singer?

45
00:03:28,550 --> 00:03:30,750
I’m here today

46
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:33,720
because I have something to ask you.

47
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,670
Do you know

48
00:03:37,670 --> 00:03:39,440
the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

49
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,580
I have never heard of it.

50
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:47,170
What’s the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

51
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:53,600
Madam, let’s not do this the hard way.

52
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:54,600
Go.

53
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:19,270
With your current power,

54
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:21,520
I’m afraid you can’t protect everyone
in Qiaoyun House.

55
00:04:21,520 --> 00:04:22,640
That’s enough!

56
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,930
Shen Tianshu.

57
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:30,340
Believe it or not,

58
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,750
I only know
that the Color of Ocean and Heaven

59
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,750
is a huge place of treasure.

60
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:35,750
That’s only because

61
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,520
I heard some elders talked about it.

62
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:41,080
But the Color of Ocean and Heaven
concerns the world.

63
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,360
I really don’t know

64
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,520
where it is

65
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,710
and what’s inside.

66
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,370
Is it?

67
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,870
Madam, you’d better tell me the truth.

68
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,270
Or else, Yuyi Troupe will never

69
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:57,140
perform again.

70
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:01,670
No matter how you threaten me with them,

71
00:05:01,670 --> 00:05:03,760
I have nothing else to tell you.

72
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,120
Shen Tianshu, I need to warn you.

73
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,760
Don’t be too wild.

74
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,040
This is Hengyang,

75
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,110
not your Demons Manor.

76
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:14,270
The garrison of Lord Gantang

77
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,730
is not far from Hengyang.

78
00:05:16,790 --> 00:05:18,040
If you have to

79
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:20,570
make a scene today,

80
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:23,990
my Yuyi Troupe will be there for you!

81
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,400
Good.

82
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:34,290
I will take your words this time.

83
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,860
Sorry for bothering you.

84
00:05:56,070 --> 00:06:00,010
I’ll come to enjoy the Yuyi Troupe’s
performance some other day.

85
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,480
Any time.

86
00:06:09,550 --> 00:06:11,610
Master, take the medicine.

87
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:29,440
Master, Mr. Qian Suiyou
wants to see you.

88
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,230
You may leave.

89
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,000
What’s the matter?

90
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:42,160
Thank you for saving Fei.

91
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,820
My appreciation is beyond words.

92
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,340
I’ll be at your disposal

93
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,080
if the Yuyi Troupe needs me.

94
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,570
You don’t need to thank me.

95
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:54,060
I didn’t do it for you.

96
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,390
Back then,

97
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:01,090
Zhou Fei’s grandfather
was my good friend.

98
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,020
My friend’s granddaughter was injured.

99
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,460
How could I stand by?

100
00:07:07,550 --> 00:07:09,040
No matter who you did it for,

101
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,120
you still did me a big favor.

102
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:16,780
You seem to have deep feelings
for Miss Zhou.

103
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,790
All right.

104
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,620
Let’s drop the empty gesture.

105
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,950
There is something

106
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:31,800
that I want to know.

107
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,670
Madam, please go ahead.

108
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,550
Recently I heard

109
00:07:40,550 --> 00:07:42,570
there is some turbulence

110
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:45,950
relevant to the descendants
of South Blade.

111
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,230
I think you should have gone through

112
00:07:47,230 --> 00:07:48,720
those things.

113
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:51,730
That’s what you are talking about.

114
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,440
I would like to know

115
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,070
the details of the whole story

116
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,520
and the truth.

117
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:01,180
Some time ago,

118
00:08:01,670 --> 00:08:04,330
Timber Wolf of Demons, Shen Tianshu
showed up in Four-guardian Mountain.

119
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,140
Then Huo’s Manor suffered an accident.

120
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,720
Huo Liantao fled away.

121
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,030
And Old Master Huo passed away.

122
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,920
Shen Tianshu?

123
00:08:16,550 --> 00:08:18,430
Why did he show up
in Four-guardian Mountain?

124
00:08:19,670 --> 00:08:20,790
I heard

125
00:08:20,790 --> 00:08:22,160
that he covets Huo’s kicking techniques,

126
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,550
so he went to kill them.

127
00:08:23,550 --> 00:08:24,620
But I don’t think

128
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:27,720
the rumors are true.

129
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,540
He is the Lord of Demons Manor.

130
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,230
There is no way he would lay his eyes on

131
00:08:31,230 --> 00:08:33,300
Huo’s special kicking techniques.

132
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:37,380
By the way,

133
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:39,390
there is another thing.

134
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,920
After the death of General Wang Lin,

135
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:43,110
his family members
were robbed and killed.

136
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,040
Who sent the killer?

137
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,040
The Blessed Dog,

138
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,390
Qiu Tianjin.

139
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,940
This is confusing.

140
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,510
Yeah.

141
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,360
They are just orphans and widows.

142
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:11,020
Why would he send a big falcon
to hunt them down?

143
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,070
So?

144
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,390
The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

145
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:21,790
I’m afraid the people of Demons Manor

146
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:24,350
have been looking for it
for a long time.

147
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:26,740
Shen Tianshu got nothing useful today.

148
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:28,520
I’m afraid there will be

149
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,760
a bloody storm.

150
00:09:33,590 --> 00:09:34,750
That’s ridiculous.

151
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:39,030
It’s despicable to

152
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,840
harm the innocent

153
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,930
just for the hearsay.

154
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:46,080
There are people killing to get it.

155
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,350
But they don’t know

156
00:09:47,350 --> 00:09:50,130
the Color of Ocean and Heaven
is useless to them.

157
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:56,350
If everyone thinks like you do,

158
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,530
the world can be at peace.

159
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:07,320
When Shen Tianshu mentioned
the Color of Ocean and Heaven,

160
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,590
you didn’t seem to be surprised.

161
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,560
Who do you belong to?

162
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:17,780
Wang Lin?

163
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,010
No.

164
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,480
You are Zhou Yitang’s person.

165
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,760
My surname is Xie.

166
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,970
My name is Yun.

167
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,130
I’m Xie Yun.

168
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:35,340
Xie Yun?

169
00:10:37,230 --> 00:10:38,320
It’s getting late.

170
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,530
I’ll leave you to rest.

171
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:41,070
Thanks again.

172
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:42,820
I won’t see you out.

173
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,270
Xie Yun.

174
00:10:55,540 --> 00:11:00,980
<i>Qiaoyun House</i>

175
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,880
Fei, you are awake!

176
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:32,090
How are you feeling?

177
00:11:35,590 --> 00:11:37,200
How’s Madam Nichang doing?

178
00:11:38,470 --> 00:11:39,230
Madam Nichang

179
00:11:39,230 --> 00:11:41,000
took the secret pill
made by Yuyi Troupe.

180
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,670
She is resting

181
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:42,760
in seclusion these days.

182
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:43,840
She should be fine.

183
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:46,080
Rest assured.

184
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,110
Just get better,

185
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:49,140
only in this way won’t you
waste Madam’s efforts.

186
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:58,500
Did Shen Tianshu come?

187
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,960
What Madam Nichang said is true.

188
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,790
Shen Tianshu has got
the information here.

189
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:05,980
He probably won’t come again.

190
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,820
Seriously, how are you feeling now?

191
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:13,850
Are you sure you are okay?

192
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:17,760
Does it still hurt?

193
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,910
Are you all right?

194
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,710
You are energetic now.

195
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:25,800
You should be fine.

196
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:29,420
I’m thirsty.

197
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,530
I’ll get some water for you.

198
00:13:06,470 --> 00:13:07,370
I’m hungry.

199
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:10,440
Let’s go. I’ll take you to the tea house
to grab a bite.

200
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,150
I’ll get your clothes for you.
Wait for me.

201
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:25,030
How long did I sleep?

202
00:13:27,820 --> 00:13:33,540
<i>Fortress of the Forty-Eight</i>

203
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:50,410
Madam.

204
00:13:57,860 --> 00:14:02,740
<i>The Secret Service defected</i>

205
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:16,150
Sir, do you have rooms?

206
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:17,470
Welcome.

207
00:14:17,470 --> 00:14:18,710
We are the only one inn

208
00:14:18,710 --> 00:14:20,110
within a radius of dozens of miles.

209
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:21,900
Well...

210
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:29,910
One good room!

211
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:30,850
-Two rooms!
-Two rooms!

212
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,880
Two rooms.

213
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:38,470
That’s not enough for two rooms.

214
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:44,640
Waiter!

215
00:14:45,350 --> 00:14:47,530
Two good rooms!

216
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,400
No problem. I’m coming!

217
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,410
Sirs, please go upstairs!

218
00:14:56,420 --> 00:15:00,060
<i>Hongfu Inn</i>

219
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,400
I’m done. Come in.

220
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:30,910
What a beauty.

221
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,590
My heart aches

222
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:34,420
at the sight of you.

223
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,190
Where are my clothes?

224
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:50,660
Why do you want me to dress like this?

225
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,930
Where are my clothes?

226
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:57,030
Your clothes are dirty.

227
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:58,410
It’s inappropriate to wear them.

228
00:15:58,910 --> 00:16:00,350
You look good

229
00:16:00,350 --> 00:16:01,480
in this dress.

230
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,350
Stop watching me. Let’s go.

231
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:13,520
Do you want to go out with this hair?

232
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,440
Or what?

233
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,230
Come on, let me comb your hair.

234
00:16:16,230 --> 00:16:17,230
Sit down.

235
00:16:17,230 --> 00:16:18,400
Let me comb your hair.

236
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:22,440
Yun.

237
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,590
You know,

238
00:16:23,590 --> 00:16:25,580
I hate to see a beauty being wasted.

239
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:28,140
Tell me,

240
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:29,660
what kind of hairstyle do you want?

241
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:32,590
Cross Bun?

242
00:16:32,590 --> 00:16:33,760
Feitian Bun?

243
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,440
Or

244
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:40,020
Lingyun Bun?

245
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,110
How about this?

246
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:48,020
The Falling Bun is also pretty.

247
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,790
You need to move less
after I get you this hairstyle.

248
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:53,760
Otherwise, it will get loose in a while.

249
00:17:14,350 --> 00:17:16,280
Mr. Xie.

250
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:19,280
Even you know how to dress up a beauty,

251
00:17:19,280 --> 00:17:21,550
you don’t need to
practice your skill by me.

252
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,400
I have no ambitions.

253
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,640
I don’t want to be a scholar

254
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:35,150
nor a general.

255
00:17:35,150 --> 00:17:36,790
I just want to be a hairdresser

256
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:38,620
to comb my future wife’s hair.

257
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:43,280
How is it?

258
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:51,830
It’s ugly.

259
00:17:53,310 --> 00:17:54,800
I think it’s pretty.

260
00:18:03,810 --> 00:18:04,710
I mean,

261
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:07,640
why do you have to wear this?

262
00:18:08,230 --> 00:18:09,950
You finally dress up

263
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:11,160
and you have to cover yourself?

264
00:18:12,950 --> 00:18:14,490
It’s like walking at night
in fancy clothes.

265
00:18:15,190 --> 00:18:16,290
It’s too ugly.

266
00:18:20,710 --> 00:18:21,370
Fine.

267
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:22,970
Don’t just eat.

268
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:24,400
The clothes I borrowed

269
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,110
would break if you keep eating.

270
00:18:26,110 --> 00:18:27,280
That’s because

271
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:28,710
you borrowed such a dress.

272
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:29,940
I feel awkward.

273
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:33,000
I think it’s pretty.

274
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,880
I mean,

275
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,680
don’t just eat.

276
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,350
You escaped from death this time.

277
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,640
Have you reflected on it?

278
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,950
Will you still pretend
to be tough again?

279
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:53,510
Do you hear me?

