00:45:39,080 --> 00:45:40,430
When did I say I am?

836
00:45:40,430 --> 00:45:42,040
Then why are you so clear about

837
00:45:42,040 --> 00:45:43,210
Master Li’s personal life?

838
00:45:43,840 --> 00:45:45,760
Because he is my grandfather.

839
00:45:45,760 --> 00:45:46,950
You call him your grandfather.

840
00:45:46,950 --> 00:45:48,840
And you said you are not
a descendant of South Blade.

841
00:45:48,840 --> 00:45:50,040
You want to fool me?

842
00:45:50,520 --> 00:45:52,600
He is my grandfather,
not your grandfather.

843
00:45:52,600 --> 00:45:54,840
I can say whatever I want.
It’s none of your business.

844
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:56,390
Listen,

845
00:45:56,390 --> 00:45:58,320
if you dare to touch me,

846
00:45:58,320 --> 00:46:00,520
the entire Fortress of the Forty-Eight
will never let you go!

847
00:46:00,520 --> 00:46:01,360
I don’t care!

848
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:04,280
Why do you pull your blade that rashly?

849
00:46:04,280 --> 00:46:05,800
How can you treat a girl like that?

850
00:46:14,010 --> 00:46:17,520
♪Stars flow like river♪

851
00:46:18,580 --> 00:46:22,180
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

852
00:46:22,750 --> 00:46:26,820
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

853
00:46:27,070 --> 00:46:30,710
♪I will never be alone♪

854
00:46:30,710 --> 00:46:34,830
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

855
00:46:35,250 --> 00:46:39,680
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

856
00:46:40,340 --> 00:46:44,900
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

857
00:46:45,130 --> 00:46:49,760
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

858
00:46:49,950 --> 00:46:53,780
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

859
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:58,690
♪When I go across the world for you♪

860
00:46:58,950 --> 00:47:02,690
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

861
00:47:03,020 --> 00:47:08,110
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

862
00:47:08,110 --> 00:47:12,050
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

863
00:47:12,050 --> 00:47:16,580
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

864
00:47:17,200 --> 00:47:24,300
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

865
00:47:25,040 --> 00:47:29,670
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

